<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:14:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>公报草案称北约抨击中国对俄罗斯的支持，支持乌克兰全面一体化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/nato-slams-china-over-russia-support-backs-full-integration-ukraine-draft-2024-07-10/</link><description>路透社周三看到的一份联合公报草案显示，北约盟国将承诺支持乌克兰走上“不可逆转的一体化道路”，并呼吁中国停止对俄罗斯对基辅发动战争的一切支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:09:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/nato-slams-china-over-russia-support-backs-full-integration-ukraine-draft-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>报告称德国已达成协议削减华为在 5G 无线网络中的角色</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/germany-deal-cut-huaweis-role-5g-wireless-network-report-says-2024-07-10/</link><description>据多家德国媒体周三报道，德国政府和移动运营商已原则上同意采取措施，在未来五年内逐步将中国科技公司的组件排除在德国 5G 无线网络之外。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 13:33:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/germany-deal-cut-huaweis-role-5g-wireless-network-report-says-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国和墨西哥采取行动阻止中国规避关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-mexico-move-thwart-china-circumvention-us-steel-aluminum-tariffs-2024-07-10/</link><description>美国和墨西哥周三宣布了新措施，以实施北美钢铁“熔化和浇注”标准，打击中国和其他通过墨西哥运输产品的国家规避美国钢铁和铝关税的行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 13:21:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-mexico-move-thwart-china-circumvention-us-steel-aluminum-tariffs-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国称印度无权开发有争议的边境地区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/china-says-india-has-no-right-carry-out-development-arunachal-pradesh-2024-07-10/</link><description>中国外交部周三在回应路透社关于新德里计划在边境国家加快水电项目的报道时表示，印度无权在中国所说的藏南地区进行开发。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 11:59:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/china-says-india-has-no-right-carry-out-development-arunachal-pradesh-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国最大汽车制造商上汽集团因销售低迷而重组领导层</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-biggest-automaker-saic-reshuffles-leadership-amid-sluggish-sales-2024-07-10/</link><description>上汽集团总裁王晓秋在领导层改组中当选为董事长，这家中国最大的汽车制造商正在应对国内市场销售低迷和欧盟面临的高额关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 11:09:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-biggest-automaker-saic-reshuffles-leadership-amid-sluggish-sales-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国与巴西试行牛肉追溯计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/land-use-biodiversity/china-brazil-try-out-beef-traceability-plan-2024-07-10/</link><description>官方媒体周三表示，全球最大的牛肉进口国中国和最大的牛肉供应国巴西将设立一项试点计划，作为使牛肉生产更加可持续的努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 11:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/land-use-biodiversity/china-brazil-try-out-beef-traceability-plan-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>禽流感病毒株：它们在全球哪些地方传播？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/bird-flu-strains-spread-around-globe-2024-07-10/</link><description>今年，禽流感在美国奶牛中出现前所未有的传播，公共卫生官员对此保持警惕。该国四名乳制品工人的检测结果也呈阳性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 10:17:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/bird-flu-strains-spread-around-globe-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>随着投资者押注政府支出，太空初创公司的资金继续复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/space-startups-funding-continues-recover-investors-bet-government-spending-2024-07-10/</link><description>英国投资公司 Seraphim Space 的数据显示，4 月至 6 月，太空初创公司吸引了 24.1 亿美元的全球投资，标志着融资连续第三个季度增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 10:10:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/space-startups-funding-continues-recover-investors-bet-government-spending-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国称黄岩岛水域“非常好”，驳回菲律宾的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-scarborough-shoal-waters-excellent-dismisses-philippine-concerns-2024-07-10/</link><description>就在菲律宾指责中国渔民破坏海洋环境几个月后，中国关于黄岩岛争议渔场周围海域的一份报告认为该海域水质优良，珊瑚礁健康。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 09:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-scarborough-shoal-waters-excellent-dismisses-philippine-concerns-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾空军参加在澳大利亚举行的多国军演</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-air-force-joins-multi-nation-war-games-australia-2024-07-10/</link><description>菲律宾空军周三抵达澳大利亚北部，这是其六十年来的首次海外部署，与美国和澳大利亚战斗机一起进行战斗训练，之际南海与中国的紧张局势加剧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 09:26:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-air-force-joins-multi-nation-war-games-australia-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，随着消费下滑，中国第二季度GDP复苏可能失去动力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-gdp-recovery-likely-lost-steam-q2-consumption-sags-2024-07-10/</link><description>由于消费需求低迷，中国经济第二季度同比增长可能为 5.1%，较前三个月的强劲开局有所放缓，这使得人们对北京需要推出更多刺激措施的预期仍不减。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 08:44:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-gdp-recovery-likely-lost-steam-q2-consumption-sags-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国加强对四大会计师事务所的审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-dials-up-scrutiny-big-four-audit-firms-after-evergrande-probe-sources-say-2024-07-10/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，中国财政部正在对四大审计公司为本土企业所做的工作进行更严格的检查，原因是担心审计机构在发现企业不当行为方面做得不够。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 08:41:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-dials-up-scrutiny-big-four-audit-firms-after-evergrande-probe-sources-say-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>副部长表示波兰将采取必要措施结束白俄罗斯边境危机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/poland-will-do-what-is-needed-end-belarus-border-crisis-says-deputy-minister-2024-07-10/</link><description>一名国防部副部长表示，波兰将尽一切努力解决其与白俄罗斯边境的移民危机，华沙正在权衡可能包括关闭边境在内的选择。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 08:40:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/poland-will-do-what-is-needed-end-belarus-border-crisis-says-deputy-minister-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>商务部称中方将调查欧盟调查是否构成贸易壁垒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-investigate-if-eu-probes-constitute-trade-barriers-says-commerce-ministry-2024-07-10/</link><description>中国商务部周三表示，中国将审查欧盟对中国企业的调查是否构成“贸易壁垒”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 08:17:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-investigate-if-eu-probes-constitute-trade-barriers-says-commerce-ministry-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车在中国销量下滑，奥迪步履蹒跚，面临压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-shares-down-after-possible-brussels-plant-closure-profit-warning-2024-07-10/</link><description>大众汽车股价周三下跌，此前隔夜发布盈利预警，部分原因是奥迪工厂可能关闭，以及中国市场造成的第二季度销量下降 3.8%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 07:10:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-shares-down-after-possible-brussels-plant-closure-profit-warning-2024-07-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>